  <name>RemoteJuggler</name>
  <summary>Git identity management for multi-account workflows</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      RemoteJuggler helps developers manage multiple git identities across GitHub,
      GitLab, and other providers. It handles SSH key switching, GPG signing
      configuration, and credential management seamlessly.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Switch between git identities with a single click</li>
      <li>Automatic identity detection based on repository remote URL</li>
      <li>GPG signing configuration per identity</li>
      <li>YubiKey/FIDO2 hardware key support</li>
      <li>Integration with system keychain for credential storage</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">dev.tinyland.RemoteJuggler.desktop</launchable>
